\end_inset

, the curve in red is 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{p}(t)=\left[\begin{array}{ccc}
\lambda_{1}(t) & \lambda_{2}(t) & 1\end{array}\right]^{T}$
\end_inset

basis functions 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}(t)$
\end_inset

, 
