\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Note also that any permutation of rows of A will also be a global minimizer
 for the problem.
 In other words, if 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
lambda_i is the distance
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
iff for univariate
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Note how all the colums of A sum up to 1.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
