 to be the smallest (irregular) triangle that encloses the 
\begin_inset Formula $2^{nd}$
\end_inset

-order polynomial curve in red.
 On the right, the simplex found using the Bezier Basis.
 The ratio between the two volumes is guaranteed to be 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{V_{MINVO}}{V_{Berns}}\approx0.7697$
