\begin_layout Section
Matrices found
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The matrices found are given in the table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "tab:table_matrices"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
 The results for 
\begin_inset Formula $n=3$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $n=4$
\end_inset

 for the MINVO basis are given up to 3 significant digits.
 Note that for both the MINVO basis and the Bezier basis, 
\begin_inset Formula $t\in[-1,1]$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

